<div class="game_area_description" id="game_area_description">
 <h2>
  About This Game
 </h2>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Keine's Expanding Class! Is a Touhou word puzzle fangame based on the classic game "Hangman", where Keine-Sensei will test your knowledge! Each round Keine will think of a word and present you a hint on what it is. Then you must guess the word one letter at a time, but guess too many incorrect letters and the game is over! Complete words letter by letter until you've satisfied Keine Sensei! Each time you guess a word correctly her pride in you as her student grows!
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  After spending too much time goofing off in class, your classroom teacher Keine Kamishirasawa has decided to punish you by making you stay after class with more class work! Being the kind teacher that she is though, she's decided to format the classes as a fun word game to help you pay attention... but there's something weird happening that's already grabbing your attention!?
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video autoplay="" class="bb_img" height="540" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3894520/extras/2c7f7db3544c22d25a08e91630d98076.poster.avif?t=1777406836" width="960">
    <source src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3894520/extras/2c7f7db3544c22d25a08e91630d98076.webm?t=1777406836" type="video/webm; codecs=vp9"/>
    <source src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3894520/extras/2c7f7db3544c22d25a08e91630d98076.mp4?t=1777406836" type="video/mp4"/>
   </video>
  </span>
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <strong>
   Key Features:
  </strong>
 </p>
 <ul class="bb_ul">
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    <strong>
     A game for Touhou fans of all levels and non-Touhou fans alike
    </strong>
    ! Customize the word pool by picking your favorite games so familiar Touhou characters, songs and locations appear as words, or just test your knowledge of real English words! Make your own playlist of words to keep the game fair and fresh!
   </p>
  </li>
 </ul>
 <ul class="bb_ul">
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    <strong>
     4 selectable difficulty levels, with six unlockable ones!
    </strong>
    Each increasing difficulty expands the word pool to include more difficult and obscure words. Expect some gimmicks on specific difficulties that might make things balloon out of control! How far can you get before it gets too much for you?
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    Challenge yourself through a series of increasingly difficult levels on your chosen difficulty, as well as an unlockable endless mode! Each level has its own playlist of remixed Touhou songs!
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    Things getting too difficult? Keine sensei can help! Use spell cards during gameplay to take advantage of Keine's ability to consume history, restarting the current round like all your mistakes didn't happen!
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    Challenge yourself to clear stages in the fastest time possible with recorded times for every level and difficulty!
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    Unlock new customizable content as you progress, including new teachers and soundtracks!
   </p>
  </li>
 </ul>
</div>
<div class="game_area_description" id="game_area_content_descriptors">
 <h2>
  Mature Content Description
 </h2>
 <p>
  The developers describe the content like this:
 </p>
 <p>
  <i>
   This game contains breast expansion content. Each word puzzle completed in game results in the on screen character's breasts growing in size. Her breasts can potentially grow to an extreme size.
  </i>
 </p>
</div>
